    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained. Mechanically, it is very reliable; the engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts exactly as it should without any hesitation. The interior is clean and has been cared for, though you will find some minor, expected wear on the driver's seat and touchpoints. On the exterior, the paint still holds a nice shine, but there are a few small stone chips on the hood and a light scratch on the rear bumper from normal use. It has a solid service history and is ready to be driven daily without any immediate concerns.",
      "price": 35500.0,
